headline: IBD Stock Of The Day Positioned To 'Substantially Absorb' Trump Tariffs; Eyes Buy Point
summary: Cheesecake Factory stock, amid an 11% rally since Q1 earnings, traded near a traditional buy point in Thursday's stock market.
